256
00:15:30.095 --> 00:15:31.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああ ホントだ

257
00:15:31.597 --> 00:15:33.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ぐーるぐる回ってんじゃん

258
00:15:33.724 --> 00:15:35.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
